gtruth.py - ground truth generation or validation tool
hyperplane2.py - L2-norm based classification
createb.py - Blob extractor based on bounding box information given by tesseract
translit2.sh - handy way to decode transliterated tamil character classes in OCR (used with groundtruth
file)

Note:
The term hyperplane2 to name hyperplane2.py is a misnomer, so please ignore it. 
